WeBuyCars has announced that it is opening a new warehouse in Johannesburg South. The car dealer said that it would host a grand opening for its new location on 6 February 2019. WeBuyCars shared images of the new warehouse in Aeroton, Johannesburg, which offers a large floor space for second-hand vehicles along with on-site sales staff. At the end of 2017, WeBuyCars opened the biggest car showroom in Africa and it has continued to grow at a rapid pace. Photos of the new WeBuyCars warehouse in Johannesburg South are posted below.              